    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels so heavy, you know? like i've spent my whole life walking and looking at things, but now i'm just tired of the noise. the world is so loud and constant. a quiet ending sounds so much better than more traveling. do you think it's weird to want to just... stop? everything?",
